window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Dominic Thompson becomes an Infernal dungeon core and is given one task: honor the dark goddess by killing adventurers.</p> <p>Choosing an avatar is merely the first step. To become the greatest, he must make the other dungeon cores submit to him. And that means shattering their jeweled hearts.</p> <p>Or seducing their avatars.</p> <p>Lucky for Dom, the dungeon’s avatars are beautiful monster girls. But they’re also the fiercest warriors in the realms, and there’s a fine line between murder and seduction.</p> <p>Warning: Contains harem elements and mature content.</p>"; 
